data.description: This is one of a kind home in a quiet neighborhood, it is 1st owner owned and a very well kept home. It is a two story, four bedroom and three full bathroom home situated in a Cul de sac. It is a Gated community with no back door neighbors. Updated the HVAC system Coil in July 2023, it comes with 10 Yr warranty. New floor 2022. There is an extra wide driveway for six car parking. Painted the interior 2017. Got the fence extended from the builders 2007 when bought the house. Changed the fenced partially in 2023 , there are two entrances for the fence. Close to Hwy 6 and Hwy 59. Don’t miss a chance to own this remarkably convenient home.
